children.subject: Roughly when will we know whether or not we've been nominated?

history.content:
Dear Students,

 

This is a call for nomination to participate in the Global Young Scientists Summit. As a department we can nominate up to 3 participants and 3 viewers. Please visit the following website for more information on the Global Young Scientists Summit. (https://www.nrf.gov.sg/gyss/home)

 

I apologize for the short notice. Quick turnaround time is required. To be considered for the nominations you must be an EECS or CS Major.

You will need to email your resume and SID to me by Noon tomorrow (September 24th).  My email is antoined@eecs.berkeley.edu.

 

Sincerely,

 

Antoine Davis
